description: Returns a description of the specified consumable resource.

parameters.name: consumableResource
parameters.description: The name or ARN of the consumable resource whose description will be returned.

nested_items.name: consumableResourceName
nested_items.description: The name of the consumable resource.

nested_items.name: consumableResourceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the consumable resource.

nested_items.name: totalQuantity
nested_items.description: The total amount of the consumable resource that is available.

nested_items.name: inUseQuantity
nested_items.description: The amount of the consumable resource that is currently in use.

nested_items.name: availableQuantity
nested_items.description: The amount of the consumable resource that is currently available to use.

nested_items.name: resourceType
nested_items.description: Indicates whether the resource is available to be re-used after a job completes. Can be one of:

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The Unix timestamp (in milliseconds) for when the consumable resource was created.
